title: Olive et Gourmando
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Western, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Little lunch and sandwich bar with an eclectic menu. Go early for lunch as the little dining room fills quickly. Try the viva la vegan sandwich, fresh salads, and pastries. Owned and operated by the people who bake and do menu planning.
